data.description: Situated on idyllic Washington Street, in the heart of Duxbury, you will find this charming estate. Set on over an acre of gorgeous manicured grounds, encompassing a 3 bedroom main house, a 1 bedroom guest house and a carriage house. Step inside the main house, where an exquisite blend of old + new welcomes you. NEW gourmet kitchen with white cabinetry + quartz countertops is a showstopper. Living room with built-in cabinets + access to NEW wrap around porch. Dining room with window seat + plenty of room for a crowd. Sun splashed family room with fireplace. First floor bedroom/office, full bath + laundry room. Second floor boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, inclusive of a primary suite. Main house has been extensively renovated with new windows, new roof, new exterior doors, HVAC, patio with built-in firepit and outdoor shower, new sprinkler system, new driveway and SO much more. Guest house has been renovated. Carriage house is partially renovated. Walk to local shops + Shipyard beach!
